<chapter>
    <section xml:id="test-v3">
        <para>
            You can encode sets into a blob.
            Do something with <code>type</code> to
            <code>application/json</code> and JSON strings in a
            <code>blob</code>. Example:
        </para>
        <programlisting>"blob": {
        "default": false
    }</programlisting>
        <para>
            Or:
        </para>
        <programlisting> "blob": {
        "foobar_user": [
            "role:compute-user"
        ]
    }</programlisting>
    </section>
